sequenceDiagram
  participant AUI as Admin UI
  participant G as Gateway
  participant AS as Admin Service
  participant US as User Service
  participant DB as PostgreSQL
  participant AN as Analytics Service

  AUI->>G: PUT /api/admin/books/:bookId/validation
  G->>AS: update validation status
  AS->>US: verify admin token
  US-->>AS: admin authorized
  AS->>DB: upsert BookValidation
  AS->>DB: create ModerationLog
  AS->>AN: emit BOOK_VALIDATION_UPDATED
  AS-->>AUI: validation record
